@startuml
title Retrieval Pipeline of the Implemented AI-Assisted Knowledge System

skinparam style strictuml
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam ArrowColor #2f4f4f
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2

actor "User" as User

rectangle "Knowledge Chat API" as Chat
rectangle "Query Embedding\n(Ollama)" as Emb
database "Chroma Vector Store" as Chroma
rectangle "Lexical Search\n(KB Reader)" as Lex
rectangle "Context Builder" as Ctx
rectangle "LLM Generation\n(Ollama)" as LLM
rectangle "Answer + Sources" as Out

User --> Chat : query

Chat --> Emb : embed query
Emb --> Chroma : vector search
Chroma --> Ctx : vector chunks

Chat --> Lex : fallback search
Lex --> Ctx : lexical docs

Ctx --> LLM : grounded prompt
LLM --> Out : answer
Chat --> Out : source metadata
Out --> User : answer + sources

note right of Chat
Vector-first retrieval is the primary path.
Lexical search is used when vector retrieval
is unavailable or insufficient.
end note

@enduml